elements.title: The Rookie
elements.actors: Nathan Fillion, Alyssa Diaz, Richard T. Jones
elements.description: A life-changing incident pushes a 45-year-old man to chase his dream of becoming a cop. But he must prove himself to his LAPD superiors to make the cut.

elements.title: Young Sheldon
elements.actors: Nathan Fillion, Alyssa Diaz, Richard T. Jones
elements.description: Brilliant yet awkward 9-year-old Sheldon Cooper lands in high school where his smarts leave everyone stumped in this The Big Bang Theory spin-off.

elements.title: Avatar The Last Airbender
elements.actors: Nathan Fillion, Alyssa Diaz, Richard T. Jones
elements.description: A young boy known as the Avatar must master the four elemental powers to save a world at war — and fight a ruthless enemy bent on stopping him.

elements.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
elements.actors: Nathan Fillion, Alyssa Diaz, Richard T. Jones
elements.description: From his pineapple home base under the sea, SpongeBob and his friends, including his meowing pet snail Gary, get into memorable misadventures.

elements.title: Yellowstone
elements.actors: Nathan Fillion, Alyssa Diaz, Richard T. Jones
elements.description: The owner of Montana's largest ranch, John Dutton, defends a vanishing way of life as business interests and politicians scheme to force him out.

elements.title: House, M.D.
elements.actors: Nathan Fillion, Alyssa Diaz, Richard T. Jones
elements.description: Hugh Laurie stars as Dr. Gregory House, an ornery physician who loathes his patients but is a genius at treating mysterious ailments.

elements.title: Suits
elements.actors: Nathan Fillion, Alyssa Diaz, Richard T. Jones
elements.description: After impressing a slick lawyer with his razor-sharp mind, a college dropout scores a coveted associate job, even though he has no legal credentials.

elements.title: Lucifer
elements.actors: Nathan Fillion, Alyssa Diaz, Richard T. Jones
elements.description: Bored with being the Lord of Hell, the devil relocates to Los Angeles, where he opens a nightclub and forms a connection with a homicide detective.

elements.title: Queen of Tears
elements.actors: Nathan Fillion, Alyssa Diaz, Richard T. Jones
elements.description: The queen of department stores and her small-town husband weather a marital crisis —until love miraculously begins to bloom again.

elements.title: Money Heist
elements.actors: Nathan Fillion, Alyssa Diaz, Richard T. Jones
elements.description: Eight thieves take hostages and lock themselves in the Royal Mint of Spain as a criminal mastermind manipulates the police to carry out his plan.
